data = pd.read_table(fold+file_)
if ('DSSR' in data.columns):
        data.drop('DSSR', axis=1, inplace=True)            
data_without_na = data.dropna()
data_sizes = []
tmp_help = {'original':{'N elements':[], 'N sites':[], '% sites':[]}, 
                 'drop NA':{'N elements':[], 'N sites':[], '% sites':[]}}

for name in names:
    tmp_help['original']['N elements'].append(np.sum(list(map(lambda x: name in x, np.array(data['pdb_chain']))))) 
    tmp_help['drop NA']['N elements'].append(np.sum(list(map(lambda x: name in x, np.array(data_without_na['pdb_chain'])))))
    tmp_help['original']['N sites'].append(np.sum(np.array(list(map(lambda x: name in x, np.array(data['pdb_chain']))))*(np.array(data['mg'])==1)))
    tmp_help['drop NA']['N sites'].append(np.sum(np.array(list(map(lambda x: name in x, np.array(data_without_na['pdb_chain']))))*(np.array(data_without_na['mg'])==1)))
    tmp_help['original']['% sites'].append(round(100*round(tmp_help['original']['N sites'][-1]/tmp_help['original']['N elements'][-1],3),1))
    tmp_help['drop NA']['% sites'].append(round(100*round(tmp_help['drop NA']['N sites'][-1]/tmp_help['drop NA']['N elements'][-1],3),1))
